{"tid":863551,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"睇下大家可唔可以在股市中短炒賺錢","createTime":"2018-10-15T16:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T12:19:15.000Z","uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"afb2c5e26c8796a71dda670138723944014102a2","tid":863551,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:27:16.000Z","msg":"為避免交大量學費<br />\n各位巴絲，不如在此POST網上模擬一次<br />\n估下今日升定跌<br />\n<br />\nExample:<br />\n2018/10/16 估<br />\n恒生指數: 升<br />\n0700: 跌<br />\n0005: 升<br />\n<br />\n過多十幾日，睇下自已的記錄，再評論自己在股票市場中短炒能否賺到錢<br />\n<br />\n估中機率<br />\n<br />\n&lt; 50% : 你都係蝕的, 短炒唔岩你<br />\n50% ~ 60% : 你好似會賺, 但計埋手續費, 應該賺唔到<br />\n60% ~ 70% : 可以試下玩下, 但牛熊窩輪或高槓桿投資要小心<br />\n70% ~ 80% : 玩牛熊窩輪或高槓桿投資都冇問題, 即日炒都得<br />\n&gt;80% :  買牛熊窩輪或高槓桿投資, 巴絲你好大機會嬴, 發達在望。"},{"pid":"02216a728830b33703e9b5ce9fb785cb69ac8afe","tid":863551,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:34:15.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"9684597c9a615665f26a83d5d553c75e22f470fa","tid":863551,"uid":31937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:37:04.000Z","msg":"2018/10/16 <br />\n恒生指數: 跌<br />\n0700: 跌<br />\n0005: 跌"},{"pid":"6b5748f9abadba8cce51ed9b66e0b27d03c0462b","tid":863551,"uid":73,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:56:42.000Z","msg":"冇撚用<br />\n唔係玩真錢個心理質素完全唔同"},{"pid":"17e8ee736434a80b6b7b6b42a522ba36e69a4cea","tid":863551,"uid":111873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"3a9f0b299e3f7f74d40a5f621adb35f873ee4c7f","tid":863551,"uid":199727,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T18:28:36.000Z","msg":"傻仔先睇機率<br />\n識玩既話 30%勝率 長遠都可以賺錢"},{"pid":"3b5fa7074029dd209449d738b882dc73a5072d26","tid":863551,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6b5748f9abadba8cce51ed9b66e0b27d03c0462b","tid":863551,"uid":73,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T